Package com.agilebank.util.logger.controller

Class AccountControllerLogger

java.lang.Object
com.agilebank.util.logger.controller.AccountControllerLogger
@Component public class AccountControllerLogger extends Object
AOP-enabled class that logs all calls to public methods of AccountController. Calls to entrance, exit and exception throwing are all logged.
Author:
jason
